---
const link = "/about/#data-processing-decisions";
---

<section class="mission">
  <h2 class="section-label">Mission</h2>
  <p class="mission-text">
    Data about Kenya is buried in PDFs, messy Excel files, poorly documented, and hard to access. Getting it ready for analysis or development is a headache. +254 extracts data from Kenyan institutions, cleans and processes it, and serves it through a plug-and-play API.
  </p>
  <a href={link} class="mission-link">How we process data <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    color: var(--color-warm-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .mission-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-regular);
    color: var(--color-warm-mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .mission-link {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: #1f6f54;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s var(--ease-out);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .mission-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #145c42;
  }

  .mission-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid #1f6f54;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
